parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel starvation issue can cause the engine to sputter, stall, or lose power, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or stranding the driver in traffic, which can be life-threatening.
symptoms: engine stalling at various times while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling or "flame out" issue can cause the vehicle to lose power and decelerate rapidly, increasing the risk of accidents, especially in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The engine shuts off while riding
the bike stalls while accelerating from a stop
the bike stalls when blipping the throttle on a downshift to rev match
the bike has no power regardless of throttle input.
